{"tid":1473850,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第39分鐘，藍絲市民終於抱怨：「老天，何解警察尚未出現？」香港警察：「哦，只係遲左39分鐘」","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:25:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T05:36:06.000Z","uid":159083,"like":73,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1feb5ebc93088c696fdf4b2934aa510b6ffb8554","tid":1473850,"uid":159083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"撥打999後的6分鐘，消防員已穿起防火衣、戴上手套抵達；抵達樓宇密集地區處理火警；香港警察在更衣室商量下午茶吃甚麼。 12分鐘，救護車亦都抵達現場；香港警察正在開始換上制服。 15分鐘，傳說中的高鐵已從西九龍站到達福田站，香港警察正在尋找手錶。 20分鐘，麥麥送都已送到府上了；香港警察一無所穫 決定放棄手錶 帶上裝備準備應付「暴徒」。 30分鐘， 消防已將火警救熄 並收拾裝備準備離開；香港警察檢查裝備時 發現忘了在警棍裝上鐵戒指 。35分鐘，報案的市民已被白衫人打得片體鱗傷 香港警察在駕車從元朗警署前往元朗港鐵站現場 。第39分鐘，藍絲市民終於抱怨：「老天，何解警察尚未出現？」香港警察：「哦，只係遲左39分鐘」"},{"pid":"85fd36398d735c8482128da24944f4de2e2d3429","tid":1473850,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc5d966b8db3ba796aa7372dc905316d166ed6d1","tid":1473850,"uid":159083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:28:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445dfefe09f9fb95fa421462e419762c0bacddd3","tid":1473850,"uid":60563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:29:40.000Z","msg":"分段啦大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412c440468195ec0aee733fc63882fbe4389cbe3","tid":1473850,"uid":29080,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:30:20.000Z","msg":"解放軍：啊，是時候在深圳集結。"},{"pid":"146f7cfa1a38bf0d2faf261c32343fff14d6bafc","tid":1473850,"uid":258327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RXX7VTz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRXX7VTz.jpg&h=5d5046b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"857e498ac